Package com.audiofetch.afaudiolib.bll.event

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApbActivatedEvent
    Triggered when the playing/connected apb has changed to a different host
    AudioFocusEvent
    Triggered by AudioManager.onAudioFocusChange by AudioController
    AudioPreferenceChangeEvent
    Triggered when a preference value used by audiofetch audio is modified
    AudioStateEvent
    This is the audio state change event, and state will be one of the defined constants for state
    AudioTypeEvent
    Returns an audio type event of either a sapa, or native value
    ChannelChangedEvent
    Triggered after the audio infrastructure has successfully switched the channel.
    ChannelSelectedEvent
    Triggered when a channel selected event should be bubbled up to the UI
    ChannelsReceivedEvent
    Triggered by AudioController with the full list of channels
    EventBus
    Wraps creation and access to the Bus class
    NoInternetDetectedEvent
    Triggered when an internet request fails to complete
    VolumeChangeEvent
    Triggered a volume change event
    WifiSpeedEvent
    Triggered when by WifiController, when the Wifi speed has dropped below, or risen above given thresholds.
    WifiStatusEvent
    Triggered when wifi status connected/disconnected, enabled/disabled
